column5: Sad sight, but that's mother nature for ya.  Definitely went through on crappy ice or the wolves and coyotes would have had her down to bones in no time.
thatd be a stinky one if you hit it with the prop lol
That is a moose? or what's left of one?
did you grab the tenderloins off it at least?
man .. i thought the dead carp I came across a few days ago was big.
She was a big girl, that's for sure.
